148,"operating_margins":0.0401,"profit_margins":0.00871,"net_income":11536000.0,"total_cash":84943000.0,"total_cash_per_share":0.157,"total_debt":211519008.0,"debt_to_equity":30.884,"enterprise_value":763736640.0,"enterprise_to_ebitda":19.777,"enterprise_to_revenue":0.577,"shares_outstanding":473877773.0,"float_shares":364623291.0,"held_pct_insiders":0.35346,"held_pct_institutions":0.0,"beta":-0.089,"fifty_two_week_high":2.46,"fifty_two_week_low":1.13,"fifty_day_average":1.5394,"two_hundred_day_avg":1.8543,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":24.9,"all_time_low":1.0,"long_business_summary":"Sundaram Multi Pap Limited designs, manufactures, and markets paper stationery products for students in India. The company offers A4/A5/A3 books, original long books, college books, hard bound books, notebooks, sketch books, lekhan books, drawing books, practical books, laboratory books, graph books, scrap books, pocketbooks, six subject books, graph and map sheets, answer books and sheets, origami paper sheets, tinted sheets, duplicate books, cash memo books, delivery challan books, conference pads, and voucher books; exercise notebooks and long books; and project books, educational paper stationery, practical papers, drawing paper, pocket notebooks, case bound books, wiro notebooks, binding books, big long books, c-ruled registers, triplicate books, cash memos, rent receipts, and scribbling pads. It also provides office/corporate stationery products, as well as printing, writing, and packaging paper products. In addition, the company offers E-CLASS, an educational content for the students of Maharashtra State Board's 1st to 10th standards for various subjects available in English, Marathi, Semi English, Hindi, and Urdu medium as per the syllabus. It sells its products under the Sundaram brand. Sundaram Multi Pap Limited was founded in 1985 and is based in Palghar, India."}}